#rad
       tan(α+2kπ)=tan α
               |    π
tan(π-α)=-tan α|tan(-- +α)=-cot α
               |    2
---------------|-------------------
               |    π
 tan(π+α)=tan α|tan(-- -α)=cot α
               |    2
#deg
        tan(α+k*360°)=tan α
tan(180°-α)=-tan α|tan(90°+α)=-cot α
------------------|-------------------
 tan(180°+α)=tan α|tan(90°-α)=cot α